<h1>7 Video Games You'll Want to Buy in August</h1>
<div class="deck">
As summer comes to a close, publishers are pushing out some must-buy games before the holiday rush. Add these gems to your shopping cart and get playing.
</div>
<aside class="byline">
<ul>
<li>
<div class="multiple-authors">
<aside class="author-byline-images hide-for-small-only">
